data.description:
PRICE REDUCED!! Explore the possibilities in this spacious 4-bedroom, 3.5-bath,
2-story home located in Maricopa. Boasting a unique attached 1/1 Guest House
and an expanded Primary Suite Retreat, this residence offers versatile living
arrangements.
The main level features a well-equipped kitchen with a gas range, double wall
ovens, and extended quartz countertops, making it perfect for hosting gatherings
and holiday dinners. The inclusion of a dedicated washer and dryer in the guest
house adds to the flexibility of the space, catering to multi-generational living or
accommodating roommates. Ascend to the second level, where a roomy loft awaits, leading to the expansive primary suite that feels like a private retreat. Two additional bedrooms and a shared bathroom provide ample space for a growing family or guests. A large laundry room adds convenience to daily living.
Step outside to the backyard, a blank canvas ready for your personal touch. Enjoy the spacious covered patio and the privacy of no rear neighbors - an ideal setting for relaxation or entertaining.
This property is an exceptional opportunity for those seeking a harmonious blend of space, privacy, and adaptability. Next-Gen living at it's best!
